She looked at Stringtra. "You look after Quickstrike.  he's going to 
need all the help he can get.  I'll go with Scorponok and find the 
rodent.  Just do me one favor, keep me posted as to what 
Quickstrike's condition is. OK?" She tried to smile a reasuring smile.
 She turned and looked at Scorponok. "Let's grab any gear we need and 
get going."
